OL,3,CRare behind-the-scenes photos of Harry
OL,4,CPotter set go under the hammer
OL,6,FA railway worker for the Hogwarts
OL,7,FExpress snuck his camera into the
OL,8,FHarry Potter set, and took more than
OL,9,F140 behind-the-scenes photos of the
OL,10,Fstars as they filmed for the movie
OL,11,Fseries.
OL,13,FThe photos taken by Graham Wood, from
OL,14,FBuxton in Derbyshire, as he shovelled
OL,15,Fcoal, are now under the hammer at
OL,16,FHansons Auctioneers.
