OL,3,CRare behind-the-scenes photos of Harry
OL,4,CPotter set go under the hammer
OL,6,FIt features photos of actors Daniel
OL,7,FRadcliffe, Rupert Grint and Emma
OL,8,FWatson, as well as call sheets from
OL,9,FHarry Potter and the Order of the
OL,10,FPhoenix, signed by members of the cast.
OL,12,FThe photos are rare because cameras
OL,13,Fwere not allowed on the soon-to-be
OL,14,Ficonic set.
OL,16,FThe collection, featuring five Harry
OL,17,FPotter films, is expected to make
OL,18,F#2,000-#3,000.
