OL,3,CRare behind-the-scenes photos of Harry
OL,4,CPotter set go under the hammer
OL,6,F"I can't say we mixed with the cast,
OL,7,Fbut those with an interest in steam
OL,8,Ftrains like Mr Weasley (Mark
OL,9,FWilliams), would come down to the
OL,10,Ffootplate for a chat."
OL,12,FHe said: "We weren't supposed to take
OL,13,Fphotos, but I managed to sneak some as
OL,14,Fwe escorted the guests onto the
OL,15,Fplatform. There were so many famous
OL,16,Fpeople in attendance.
OL,18,F"By far the nicest was Chris Eubank
OL,19,Fwho came over to thank us and say
OL,20,Fhello. He was a real gentleman."
